[
  {
    "text": "- Today we're exploring the solution,",
    "start": "0",
    "end": "1710"
  },
  {
    "text": "automated security response on AWS",
    "start": "1710",
    "end": "4200"
  },
  {
    "text": "for remediating security\nfindings, simply and quickly.",
    "start": "4200",
    "end": "7649"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm joined by Matt,",
    "start": "7650",
    "end": "9240"
  },
  {
    "text": "a principal software engineer\nfrom Intuit in California,",
    "start": "9240",
    "end": "12540"
  },
  {
    "text": "who has deployed the solution",
    "start": "12540",
    "end": "14070"
  },
  {
    "text": "to automate manual remediation processes.",
    "start": "14070",
    "end": "16770"
  },
  {
    "text": "- Thanks, Katie.",
    "start": "16770",
    "end": "17603"
  },
  {
    "text": "Intuit's mission is to power\nprosperity around the world",
    "start": "17603",
    "end": "20550"
  },
  {
    "text": "for a hundred million customers.",
    "start": "20550",
    "end": "22170"
  },
  {
    "text": "We're committed to helping our customers",
    "start": "22170",
    "end": "23910"
  },
  {
    "text": "run their financial lives with confidence,",
    "start": "23910",
    "end": "26490"
  },
  {
    "text": "using TurboTax, Credit Karma,\nQuickBooks, and MailChimp.",
    "start": "26490",
    "end": "30390"
  },
  {
    "text": "We handle lots of\nsensitive data every day.",
    "start": "30390",
    "end": "32579"
  },
  {
    "text": "Regulatory compliance is a top priority,",
    "start": "32580",
    "end": "35070"
  },
  {
    "text": "and we needed a solution\nthat would work alongside",
    "start": "35070",
    "end": "37440"
  },
  {
    "text": "our internal automated compliance platform",
    "start": "37440",
    "end": "39840"
  },
  {
    "text": "to maintain strong security posture.",
    "start": "39840",
    "end": "42030"
  },
  {
    "text": "- Well, let's dive in.",
    "start": "42030",
    "end": "43199"
  },
  {
    "text": "So at the core of this\nis AWS Security Hub,",
    "start": "43200",
    "end": "46140"
  },
  {
    "text": "which aggregates security findings",
    "start": "46140",
    "end": "48000"
  },
  {
    "text": "from multiple AWS services.",
    "start": "48000",
    "end": "50370"
  },
  {
    "text": "These findings are crucial",
    "start": "50370",
    "end": "52020"
  },
  {
    "text": "for triggering automated\nsecurity responses.",
    "start": "52020",
    "end": "55493"
  },
  {
    "text": "Amazon EventBridge is engaged",
    "start": "55493",
    "end": "57510"
  },
  {
    "text": "once a security issue is detected.",
    "start": "57510",
    "end": "59489"
  },
  {
    "text": "This service acts as the conduit",
    "start": "59490",
    "end": "61560"
  },
  {
    "text": "for initiating security remediations.",
    "start": "61560",
    "end": "63930"
  },
  {
    "text": "The actual remediation\ntasks are carried out",
    "start": "63930",
    "end": "66420"
  },
  {
    "text": "by AWS Systems Manager automation document",
    "start": "66420",
    "end": "69240"
  },
  {
    "text": "within the member account that\nhouses the affected resource.",
    "start": "69240",
    "end": "72960"
  },
  {
    "text": "This approach ensures direct",
    "start": "72960",
    "end": "74670"
  },
  {
    "text": "and efficient mitigation\nof security matters.",
    "start": "74670",
    "end": "77340"
  },
  {
    "text": "Throughout this process,",
    "start": "77340",
    "end": "78659"
  },
  {
    "text": "all actions are logged\nin Amazon CloudWatch,",
    "start": "78660",
    "end": "81720"
  },
  {
    "text": "and notifications are sent",
    "start": "81720",
    "end": "83370"
  },
  {
    "text": "via Amazon's simple notification service.",
    "start": "83370",
    "end": "85860"
  },
  {
    "text": "So, Matt, tell us about\nthe customization you did",
    "start": "85860",
    "end": "88140"
  },
  {
    "text": "in automated security response",
    "start": "88140",
    "end": "89850"
  },
  {
    "text": "to implement a rollback feature.",
    "start": "89850",
    "end": "91350"
  },
  {
    "text": "- We developed a capability that allows",
    "start": "91350",
    "end": "93450"
  },
  {
    "text": "any changes made during a\nremediation to be reversed.",
    "start": "93450",
    "end": "96719"
  },
  {
    "text": "For instance, if a change made",
    "start": "96720",
    "end": "98460"
  },
  {
    "text": "through automated security response",
    "start": "98460",
    "end": "99988"
  },
  {
    "text": "turns out to be incorrect,",
    "start": "99988",
    "end": "101940"
  },
  {
    "text": "our custom rollback\nfunction can be triggered",
    "start": "101940",
    "end": "104070"
  },
  {
    "text": "to restore the original settings.",
    "start": "104070",
    "end": "106200"
  },
  {
    "text": "This level of customization",
    "start": "106200",
    "end": "107759"
  },
  {
    "text": "allows us to respond quickly\nin our security approach,",
    "start": "107760",
    "end": "111390"
  },
  {
    "text": "ensuring robust compliance.",
    "start": "111390",
    "end": "113310"
  },
  {
    "text": "- Let's talk about how beneficial",
    "start": "113310",
    "end": "115079"
  },
  {
    "text": "this AWS solution has\nbeen to Intuit Security.",
    "start": "115080",
    "end": "117990"
  },
  {
    "text": "- The most immediate benefit",
    "start": "117990",
    "end": "119430"
  },
  {
    "text": "is that we've dramatically\nreduced the time it takes",
    "start": "119430",
    "end": "122160"
  },
  {
    "text": "to remediate our compliance\nfindings by over 80%.",
    "start": "122160",
    "end": "125430"
  },
  {
    "text": "Also, as a result,",
    "start": "125430",
    "end": "126600"
  },
  {
    "text": "we've improved our overall\ncompliance posture.",
    "start": "126600",
    "end": "129330"
  },
  {
    "text": "- Matt, thank you so much\nfor sharing your insights.",
    "start": "129330",
    "end": "132210"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you're inspired",
    "start": "132210",
    "end": "133170"
  },
  {
    "text": "by how Intuit has enhanced\ntheir security capabilities",
    "start": "133170",
    "end": "136260"
  },
  {
    "text": "and want to learn more\nabout this solution,",
    "start": "136260",
    "end": "138540"
  },
  {
    "text": "visit the AWS Solutions page.",
    "start": "138540",
    "end": "140879"
  },
  {
    "text": "Until next time, keep solving with AWS.",
